@8 = ~Breath of Cold (Evocation) 
Sphere: Elemental
Level: 2
Range: Special
Duration: Instantaneous
Casting Time: Instant
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: none

The caster breathes out an intense breath of cold. Anyone caught within range suffer 12d12 cold damage as well as be slowed for 1 & 1/2 round (save vs. breath weapons neg). This spell increases in effect as the caster gains in experience.

This spell however, does have it's side effect and will render the caster unable to initiate a conversation or cast spells 1/2 round due to the severe coldness left in the caster's throat.~


@9 = ~Fimbulwinter~
@10 = ~Fimbulwinter 
(Evocation/Conjuration/Summoning) 
Sphere: Elemental, Summoning
Level: 2
Range: Visual sight of caster
Duration: Instantaneous/8 rounds
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: None

Upon the completion of the spell, the caster invokes a lesser form of one of the most powerful natural phenomenon known throughout the realms: Fimbulwinter. In addition to the 3d18 cold damage, creatures caught within the range of the spell are slowed for 4 rounds if fails to save vs. spells. This spells also summons a pack of the fabled Wolves of Fimbulwinter, and will obey the caster for as long as they remain summoned. The spell however, cannot be casted for the next 4 rounds after.~

@11 = ~Frozen Armor~
@12 = ~Forzen Armor (Alteration) 
Sphere: Elemental
Level: 1
Range: Caster
Duration: 8 hours
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

By means of this spell, the caster is enveloped by a thin layer of icy mist and crystallizations all over her body. It effectively reducuces any physical attacks by 40%. In addition, any opponent that hits the caster with any weapons or spells within a 5' radius suffers 2d8+18 cold damage. It lasts until successfully dispelled or until the duration runs out.~

@13 = ~Hoarfrost~
@14 = ~Hoarfrost (Evocation) 
Sphere: Elemental
Level: 1
Range: Visual sight of the caster
Duration: Instantaneous
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: 30 foot radius
Saving Throw: Special

When this spell is cast, the area affected suddenly radiates with an extremely chilling wind. Creatures within the area of effect take varying cold damage as well as severely limiting their movement. Hidden opponents become partially visible as an added effect. This spell will freeze Fire Elementals, Efreet and Salamanders thus, slaying them instantly.~

